# ADC reader module configuration

config ADC_READER
	bool "Enable ADC reader module"
	default y
	help
	Single-source ADC reader for P-controller and streaming.
	Reads ADC periodically and provides shared value to consumers.

	Benefits:
	- No race condition on ADC peripheral
	- No duplicated ADC reads
	- Consistent ADC values across all consumers
	- Reduced CPU overhead
